Abjuration
Level: Clr 2 (Mystra)
Components: V, S
Casting Time: 1 action
Range: Touch
Target: Creature touched
Duration: 1 minute/level
Saving Throw: Will negates (harmless)
Spell Resistance: Yes (harmless)

The subject gains a +3 resistant bonus on saving throws against spells.
Originally created by Mystra for her faithful, other faiths now have versions of this spell.